Adedayo Akinwale President Muhammadu Buhari has said that there is deliberate spread of falsehood through the use of social media that this government is not oblivious to the suffering of Nigerians. The President disclosed this Thursday during his address to the nation, days after the mindless shooting of unarmed #EndSARS protesters at Lekki Toll Gate on Tuesday night and some other parts of the country.